ActIndian Act
SubjectSiksika Nation Global Settlement Agreement
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to ENTER INTO AND EXECUTE, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the SIKSIKA NATION GLOBAL SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the Siksika Nation; and (2) accepting the absolute surrender to Canada of all rights and interest of the specified lands.
